long_description: hicks consulting, inc. provides electrical engineering services by utilizing its technical and personnel resources to deliver innovative designs through all phases of project development. in the professional engineering industry, there is no substitute for experience. our company is involved with the design and development of construction documents and construction management. we have experience with projects designed to national electrical code (nec) and related nfpa requirements for projects located in the united states. in order to provide clients with current and up-to-date technological advances, our firm utilizes and benefits from continuing education courses, seminars, and a variety of technical periodicals. hicks consulting, inc. provides project drawings in digital format. digital drawings are prepared with autocad computer aided design/drafting (cad) software, autocad mep, autodesk revit mep. electrical models of power distribution systems are analyzed with in-house spreadsheets for small projects, and with etap for larger projects.
